nodes.text: The Imperial Prefect was the highest-ranking Imperial official on a planet not currently under the Empire's direct control.
The Prefect was the Emperor's liaison with the planetary government. Prefect Eugene Talmont wore the insignia of an admiral.
During 5 ABY, Mosh Barris worked on Garqi as an Imperial Prefect.
Most prefects were in charge of prefabricated garrison bases.
